  <brief_title>Evaluation of Tolerability of Adjuvant Cisplatin/Docetaxel in Completely Resected Stage IB/II Non-Small Cell Lung Cancer</brief_title>
  <acronym>TOLEDO</acronym>
  <official_title>Randomized Phase II Study Evaluating The Tolerability Of Adjuvant Docetaxel-based Chemotherapy For Completely Resected Stage IB-II Non-Small Cell Lung Cancer (NSCLC): Toledo Trial</official_title>
