  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to evaluate the tolerability (in terms of drug delivery and
      toxicity) of four cycles of adjuvant docetaxel plus cisplatin in patients with completely
      resected stage IB-II Non-Small Cell Lung Cancer. To avoid a selection bias, eligible patients
      will be randomised to receive cisplatin/docetaxel or cisplatin/vinorelbine.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
